dct_title_s: Map of Africa showing its most recent discoveries
dct_description_sm: Coloured map of Africa showing the most recent discoveries.
Bar scale on map given in "Miles."
Inset map: Island of St. Helena. The inset shows topographical detail and useful place names.
dct_publisher_sm: Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1867 by S. Augustus Mitchell Jr. in the Clerks Office of the District Court for the Eastern District of Pennsylvania
